{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"60d0f93d1d","title":"在反修报告会上的插话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1dc8750ca9","index":0,"year":1964,"month":9,"day":4,"articleId":"60d0f93d1d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f5639f9c58","type":"title","text":"在反修报告会上的插话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"60d0f93d1d"},{"id":"eb74a9a3fe","type":"paragraph","text":"蛇是引出来好打，还是钻黑洞里好打？（对苏斯洛天报告我们赞成发表，它不发，出了八评后引出来了）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"60d0f93d1d"},{"id":"a7566d5332","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年以来，苏联骂斯大林，我们一论、二论发表后，他就失去了主动权。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"60d0f93d1d"},{"id":"15d67fd7aa","type":"paragraph","text":"点名不光我们两家，东欧也点名了。（苏批评罗自力更生，罗回击，用我们评苏联的话）不是内部的事，正在电台上干，公开于了。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"60d0f93d1d"},{"id":"fcc5b54232","type":"paragraph","text":"控制、反控制的冲突，第一位的不是中国，而是东欧国家。（罗已作了同苏断绝经济关系的准备，自己不能制造武器，要求我国去人到罗访问，不讲话都可以使人震惊，去了不讲话，握握手都很重要）","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"60d0f93d1d"},{"id":"5ceed247d4","type":"paragraph","text":"准备两手，准备破裂，争取拖。哪天出事，不是出于意料之外。天下大势，合久必分，分久必合。（中苏关系）","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"60d0f93d1d"},{"id":"996fa9b254","type":"paragraph","text":"南昌暴动轰轰烈烈，剩下几个大人，以后发展了三十万人。长征剩下几万人，以后发展起来。山不在高。（巴西老党四方人，成立新党六千人。是四万人可靠，还是六千人可靠）","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"60d0f93d1d"},{"id":"c52ce72ae2","type":"paragraph","text":"有了修正主义，列宁主义才能方岁！","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"60d0f93d1d"},{"id":"5430e2698d","type":"paragraph","text":"不注意一定出修正主义。注意可能出，可能不出。准备出，可能不出。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"60d0f93d1d"}],"page":{"id":"0864c0463c","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"60d0f93d1d","start":128,"end":128}}}},"__N_SSG":true}